<div class="business-name-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mt-5 mb-5">
            <div class="col s12 l3">
                <div class="animated slideInBottom bg-aqua" data-spy="affix" data-offset-top="197">
                    <div class="list">
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="#">Why your name matters</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Do's and Dont's</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Our Ethics</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Free Detailed Report</a></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
            <div class="col s12 l9">
                <div class="card z-depth-2 mb-5">
                    <div class=" bg-dark lead">
                        <img src="../images/dummy-img.jpg" alt="" class="card-img-top" />
					<p>Order a name correction for your Child</p></div>
					<div id="innerBoxsection">
						<p>
							We hope you have taken your First Name and Full Name Analysis to understand the power of name and how it affects our lives. If not, we urge you to take the same on this page.
						</P>
						<p>Do also take time to read a short write-up on why names matter by <a href="/whynamesmatter">clicking here</a>.</P>
					</div>
                    <p> NaamVidya name correction service for helps you to retain an existing name and surname with minor modifications.</p>
                    <p>These minor modifications are done to ensure that your First Name, Full Name and Date of birth together provide a balanced vibration for better harmony in life.</p>
                    <p>E.g *.	Reyansh can be modified to Reiyansh<br/>
                        Barrack can be modified to Barrak<br />
                        Shadab can be modified to Shadaab
					</p>
                    <p> * The above given modification examples are for illustration purpose only. Please do not consider them as recommendation for your name.</p>
                    <p><b>SKU: Name Correction Service:</b></p>
                    <p>Suggestion of possible corrected Names to balance with your Surname and Date of Birth.<br/>
                        Suggestion of possible corrected Surname (Only if First Name Balancing is not possible).<br />
                        Online discussion (through platform) to finalise a name.<br />
                        Detailed Report on Corrected Name<br />
                        Certificate of Corrected Name Assignment from NaamVidya<br />
						<b> Price: INR 7400.00</b><br />
					</p>
                    <p> Please fill the form below to purchase this service</p>
					<hr />
                    <br />
                    <form class="order-form" style="background : #ffffff;">
                        <div>
                            <div class="form-group row">
                                <div class="col l9 m8 s12">
                                    <b style="color:#d70a61;margin-top:20px;font-size:20px;">Give us the following detail.</b>
                                    @*<strong>Give us the following detail.</strong>*@
								</div>
							</div>
                            <div class="form-group row" data-ng-show="ngshowFName">
                                <label for="example-text-input" class="col l3 m4 s12 col-form-label">First Name</label>
                                <div class="col l9 m8 s12">
                                    <input class="form-control" type="text" value="" id="example-text-input" data-ng-model="firstName" maxlength="50">
								</div>
							</div>
                            <div class="form-group row">
                                <label for="example-text-input" class="col l3 m4 s12 col-form-label">Middle Name</label>
                                <div class="col l9 m8 s12">
                                    <input class="form-control" type="text" value="" id="example-text-input" data-ng-model="middleName" maxlength="50">
                                    <span class="form-control">(if used in fullname)</span>
								</div>
							</div>
                            <div class="form-group row">
                                <label for="example-text-input" class="col l3 m4 s12 col-form-label">Last Name</label>
                                <div class="col l9 m8 s12">
                                    <input class="form-control" type="text" value="" id="example-text-input" data-ng-model="lastName" maxlength="50">
								</div>
							</div>
                            <div class="form-group row">
                                <label for="example-text-input" class="col l3 m4 s12 col-form-label">Mobile No</label>
                                <div class="col l9 m8 s12">
                                    <input class="form-control" type="text" id="example-text-input" data-ng-model="mobileno" maxlength="10">
								</div>
							</div>
                            <div class="form-group row">
                                <label for="example-text-input" class="col l3 m4 s12 col-form-label">Date of Birth</label>
                                <div class="col l9 m8 s12">
                                    <input class="form-control datepicker" type="text" value="" id="example-text-input" data-ng-model="dob">
								</div>
							</div>
                            <div class="form-group row">
                                <label for="example-email-input" class="col l3 m4 s12 col-form-label">Gender</label>
                                <div class="col l9 m8 s12">
                                    <input type="text" id="txtGender" data-ng-model="gender" style="display : none;" />
                                    <input name="mf" type="radio" value="M" id="r_m" data-ng-model="gender"><label for="r_m" class="waves-effect waves-light">Male</label>
                                    <input name="mf" type="radio" value="F" id="r_f" data-ng-model="gender"><label for="r_f" class="waves-effect waves-light">Female</label>
								</div>
							</div>
                            <div class="form-group row">
                                <div class="col l9 m8 s12">
                                    <label id="lblerrormsg">{{errormsg}}</label>
								</div>
							</div>
                            <div class="form-group row">
                                <label for="example-email-input" class="col l3 m4 s12 col-form-label"></label>
                                <div class="col l9 m8 s12">
                                    <button type="button" class="waves-effect waves-light pink btn" data-ng-click="fn_Add_To_Cart()">Add To Cart</button>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>       
					</form>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>